article.description: — Ahmed Ali had a career-high 22 points as Portland defeated William Jessup 83-73 on Saturday.
article.headline: Ali scores 22 to lead Portland past William Jessup 83-73
article.linkText: Ali scores 22 to lead Portland past William Jessup 83-73
article.story: PORTLAND, Ore. -- — Ahmed Ali had a career-high 22 points as Portland defeated William Jessup 83-73 on Saturday. Eddie Davis had 11 points and seven rebounds for Portland (1-1). Latrell Jones added 11 points. Tim Strijaous had 17 points for the Warriors. Myles Corey added 14 points. Tarren Storey-Way had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
